title: [SOLVED]Macbook Air 820-3208 11' Not turning by a/c
message: its 1.6v on a/c. so q6910 or surrounding components?

title: [SOLVED]Macbook Air 820-3208 11' Not turning by a/c
message:
First check if Q6910 lets voltage through. Dead D6912 is most likely, check if there is 6.8 R6911, if it is higher then D6912 is probably dead.
If Q6910 is letting power through check R6905 and D6905.
